<text><body>
<cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">頌古</cb:mulu><cb:div type="other">
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0782a" n="0782a"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0782a01"/><milestone unit="juan" n="9"/><cb:mulu type="卷" n="9"></cb:mulu><cb:juan fun="open" n="9"><cb:jhead>入就瑞白禪師語錄卷之九</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="J" n="0782a02"/><byline cb:type="editor">明住天台護國寺嗣法門人寂蘊編</byline>
<lb ed="J" n="0782a03"/><p cb:type="head1" xml:id="pJ26p0782a0301">頌古</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0782a04"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782a0401" rend="margin-left:2em">正偏五位。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0782a05"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782a0501">正中偏夜深玉女不成眠漁翁舉棹清波上攪動澄
<lb ed="J" n="0782a06"/>潭月一團。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0782a07"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0782a0701">偏中正萬象森羅圓古鏡物物全彰炤不差絲毫皆
<lb ed="J" n="0782a08"/>入那伽定。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0782a09"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0782a0901">正中來有無不涉絕塵埃炎天大雪飄飄墜火裏蓮
<lb ed="J" n="0782a10"/>花朵朵開。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0782a11"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0782a1101">兼中至賓主相逄天然義全憑語脈露單傳一句當
<lb ed="J" n="0782a12"/>陽明的的。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0782a13"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0782a1301">兼中到打碎髑髏真個妙劫外今時俱不拈那有毘
<lb ed="J" n="0782a14"/>盧印可寶。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0782a15"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782a1501" rend="margin-left:2em">功勳五位。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0782a16"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782a1601">本無位次絕參商也須移履下村庄六戶靈靈忘死
<lb ed="J" n="0782a17"/>捨何勞守住在枯樁　　向。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0782a18"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0782a1801">念念無私不敢迷百花叢裏看為持千紅萬紫芬芳
<lb ed="J" n="0782a19"/>好總屬東君一道施　　奉。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0782a20"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0782a2001">不居空有謾商量縱使離婁眼似盲無孔鐵簫雲外
<lb ed="J" n="0782a21"/>品不干六律與宮商　　功。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0782a22"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0782a2201">心色相交理事融權施應物道人風昨日家童頻報
<lb ed="J" n="0782a23"/>道葵花傾向日明中　　共功。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0782a24"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0782a2401">不向威音那畔行豈從今世門頭立渾然打破舊時
<lb ed="J" n="0782a25"/>窩鐵鷂鑽天沒蹤跡　　功功。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0782a26"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782a2601" rend="margin-left:2em">奪人不奪境。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0782a27"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782a2701">一樹碧桃紅似錦兩瓶金菊賽金蓮個中非是陰陽
<lb ed="J" n="0782a28"/>地不許<anchor xml:id="beg_77" type="cb-app"/>佳<anchor xml:id="end_77"/>人著眼看。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0782a29"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782a2901" rend="margin-left:2em">奪境不奪人。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0782a30"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782a3001">春風疑不到天涯二月山城未見花公子王孫徒翫
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0782b" n="0782b"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0782b01"/>賞那有紅紫帶回家。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0782b02"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782b0201" rend="margin-left:2em">人境兩俱奪。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0782b03"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782b0301">天崩地裂人民喪那有君王正令行神劍亡鋒歸寶
<lb ed="J" n="0782b04"/>匣生佛而今徒有名。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0782b05"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782b0501" rend="margin-left:2em">人境俱不奪。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0782b06"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782b0601">攜酒遊東郊山花遍地紅笑談歌舞去意氣自匆匆。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0782b07"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782b0701" rend="margin-left:2em">三玄三要。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0782b08"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782b0801">第一玄動靜不干絕眾緣更闌萬籟聲俱寂禪者徒
<lb ed="J" n="0782b09"/>勞著眼看。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0782b10"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0782b1001">第二玄威風凜凜劍光寒紅旗閃爍乾坤淨電轉星
<lb ed="J" n="0782b11"/>飛過碧天。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0782b12"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0782b1201">第三玄越州城裏倒撐船東雙橋下多裝載西郭門
<lb ed="J" n="0782b13"/>頭去復還。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0782b14"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0782b1401">朕兆未分作麼道石女頭戴紫羅帽深閨不出冷愀
<lb ed="J" n="0782b15"/>愀宮漏沉沉天未曉<note place="inline">一</note>。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0782b16"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0782b1601">一法元無萬法周喝下何曾有去留轉側木人剛半
<lb ed="J" n="0782b17"/>夜珍衣不掛柳稍頭<note place="inline">二</note>。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0782b18"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0782b1801">日出峰頭本自孤高低普炤有於無百花競秀爭光
<lb ed="J" n="0782b19"/>彩半點工夫用得麼<note place="inline">三</note>。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0782b20"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782b2001" rend="margin-left:2em">一喝如金剛王寶劍。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0782b21"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782b2101">神威凜凜倚天寒阿個男兒敢近看擬議欲將佛祖
<lb ed="J" n="0782b22"/>現人亡馬喪滿長安。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0782b23"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782b2301" rend="margin-left:2em">一喝如踞地獅子。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0782b24"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782b2401">全身獨露沖寰宇那有妖狐現本形一吼乾坤皆振
<lb ed="J" n="0782b25"/>裂個中誰是對機人。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0782b26"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782b2601" rend="margin-left:2em">一喝如探竿影艸。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0782b27"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782b2701">試將一語知端的驗彼來人有與無穿過髑髏行正
<lb ed="J" n="0782b28"/>令神嚎鬼哭兩眉<g ref="#CB09432">㤤</g>。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0782b29"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782b2901" rend="margin-left:2em">一喝不作一喝用。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0782b30"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782b3001">喝時秪麼忘消息佛祖機緣收不得野鴨湖中翻浪
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0782c" n="0782c"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0782c01"/>飛不知身上乾和濕。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0782c02"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c0201" rend="margin-left:2em">賓主歷然。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0782c03"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c0301">月色穿雲透碧霄波斯夜半舞風濤山頭白浪連天
<lb ed="J" n="0782c04"/>地石女經行俏步高。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0782c05"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c0501" rend="margin-left:2em">正法眼藏。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0782c06"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c0601">掃除空有任繁興大地山河一掌平法法頭頭開正
<lb ed="J" n="0782c07"/>眼寒崖花發不沾春。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0782c08"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c0801" rend="margin-left:2em">妙唱不干舌。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0782c09"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c0901">青松翠竹解談禪流水高山總亦然二六時中無間
<lb ed="J" n="0782c10"/>斷老僧何用口唇宣。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0782c11"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c1101" rend="margin-left:2em">死蛇驚出艸。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0782c12"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c1201">骨爛皮穿氣息無忽然撞著爪牙舒神威一振清四
<lb ed="J" n="0782c13"/>海狼煙滅盡豈躊躕。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0782c14"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c1401" rend="margin-left:2em">解針枯骨吟。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0782c15"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c1501">鐵圍山下骨一堆些兒觸著振全威驚回石女雙流
<lb ed="J" n="0782c16"/>淚至今猶自倚雲飛。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0782c17"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c1701" rend="margin-left:2em">鐵牛舞三台。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0782c18"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c1801">千載鐵牛忘水草而今放出兩岸來足伸踏破毘盧
<lb ed="J" n="0782c19"/>印尾搖掃盡九垓灰。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0782c20"/><p cb:type="head2" xml:id="pJ26p0782c2001">三墮頌<note place="inline">并問荅</note></p><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c2007" rend="margin-left:1em;inline">僧問如何是類墮。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0782c21"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c2101">師荅云觸處逍遙絲毫無染。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0782c22"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c2201">披毛戴角混塵埃足舞西風類莫該芳草垂楊俱踏
<lb ed="J" n="0782c23"/>遍渾無些子帶回來。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0782c24"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c2401" rend="margin-left:1em">問如何是隨墮。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0782c25"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c2501">荅云百花林裏過一葉不沾身。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0782c26"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c2601">聲色叢中任意遊鬨然出沒豈能收山花鳥語縱橫
<lb ed="J" n="0782c27"/>現何有纖毫染污尤。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0782c28"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c2801" rend="margin-left:1em">問如何是尊貴墮。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0782c29"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c2901">荅云不住九五位常與群臣遊。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0782c30"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0782c3001">虛寂靈源不自尊常隨六國走煙塵秦樓玩月燕邦
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0783a" n="0783a"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0783a01"/>戲到處逍遙到處人。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783a02"/><p cb:type="head2" xml:id="pJ26p0783a0201">涅槃經四生頌<note place="inline">并問荅</note></p><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a0210" rend="margin-left:1em;inline">僧問如何是不生生。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783a03"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a0301">師荅云冬至纔逢九春來百花開。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0783a04"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a0401">明淨摩尼珠本來無一物當臺鑒炤時隨處陳方色。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783a05"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a0501" rend="margin-left:1em">問如何是生生。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783a06"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a0601">荅云青山點翠。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0783a07"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a0701">忽然一陣雨溪澗長洪波枯稿悉滋潤農人笑呵呵。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783a08"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a0801" rend="margin-left:1em">問如何是生不生。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783a09"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a0901">荅云境像收歸古鑒中。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0783a10"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a1001">桃李花無豔遊人興自衰水中無月影免使費心裁。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783a11"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a1101" rend="margin-left:1em">問如何是不生不生。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783a12"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a1201">荅云石女打破鏡。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0783a13"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a1301">石女忘歸路木人何處尋杳然無影跡佛祖莫能形。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783a14"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a1401" rend="margin-left:2em">就路還家。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783a15"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a1501">觸目青黃露本真縱橫到處是家珍水底金烏天上
<lb ed="J" n="0783a16"/>口眼中童子面前人。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783a17"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a1701" rend="margin-left:2em">新<anchor xml:id="beg_78" type="cb-app"/>豐<anchor xml:id="end_78"/>曲子。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783a18"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a1801">昔日新<anchor xml:id="beg_79" type="cb-app"/>豐<anchor xml:id="end_79"/>曲無人和得齊今朝重舉似音韻果然奇。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783a19"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a1901" rend="margin-left:2em">明月印蘆花。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783a20"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a2001">蘆花開遍野明月挂中天不識其中意都言一色然。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783a21"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a2101" rend="margin-left:2em">鏡裏梅花清香墮。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783a22"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a2201">石光閃若電渴鹿逐陽燄木女害相思泥人繡花絹。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783a23"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a2301" rend="margin-left:2em">竭盡今時。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783a24"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a2401">真如心裏妄涅槃性上塵自<anchor xml:id="beg_7a" type="cb-app"/>己<anchor xml:id="end_7a"/>非堪寶佛祖是閒名。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783a25"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a2501" rend="margin-left:2em">分明月在梅花上看到梅花早<anchor xml:id="beg_7b" type="cb-app"/>已<anchor xml:id="end_7b"/>遲。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783a26"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a2601">一段風光炤眼鮮何須攜手入桃園運足<anchor xml:id="beg_7c" type="cb-app"/>已<anchor xml:id="end_7c"/>乖空劫
<lb ed="J" n="0783a27"/>旨擬尋思去隔天淵。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783a28"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a2801" rend="margin-left:2em">汾陽重陽九日菊花新。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783a29"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783a2901">義公拈出膠盆汾陽不覺粘手賴因菊底翻身不然
<lb ed="J" n="0783a30"/>甚麼開口不開口木人捧起盤兒走。</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0783b" n="0783b"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0783b01"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783b0101" rend="margin-left:2em">重陽日頌示禪人。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783b02"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783b0201">重陽九日菊花新特示三玄意旨深報爾知音禪衲
<lb ed="J" n="0783b03"/>子今朝籬菊又重芬。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783b04"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783b0401" rend="margin-left:2em">法身。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783b05"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783b0501">雲起山頭暗風生樹搖尾桃開三月花菊綻九日蕊。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783b06"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783b0601" rend="margin-left:2em">法身向上事。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783b07"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783b0701">鐵樹花開正是時忽被石女摘一枝沙神怒發須彌
<lb ed="J" n="0783b08"/>倒驚起泥龍上玉池。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783b09"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783b0901" rend="margin-left:2em">萬象之中獨露身。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783b10"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783b1001">赫赫威音外獨超萬象先明明無隱匿何處有三玄。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783b11"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783b1101" rend="margin-left:2em">法界緣起。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783b12"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783b1201">一波纔動萬波隨滴滴全彰造化機落葉梧桐秋<anchor xml:id="beg_7d" type="cb-app"/>已<anchor xml:id="end_7d"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0783b13"/>蚤百花開處鷓鴣啼須領略莫狐疑翠竹搖聲兮風
<lb ed="J" n="0783b14"/>生大野月映寒潭兮碧水畫眉。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783b15"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783b1501" rend="margin-left:1em">僧問百丈超云某甲今日辭去或有人問和尚說
<lb ed="J" n="0783b16"/>甚麼法向他道甚麼超云但道大雄山頂上虎生
<lb ed="J" n="0783b17"/>獅子兒。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783b18"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783b1801">虎生獅子兒木人唱巴歌擬議停思者卻被佛祖呵。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783b19"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783b1901" rend="margin-left:1em">僧問明炤安一藏圓光如何是體安云勞汝遠來
<lb ed="J" n="0783b20"/>僧云莫便是一藏圓光麼安云更喫一碗茶。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783b21"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783b2101">問處分明荅處彰圓光之體露堂堂春風布遍山花
<lb ed="J" n="0783b22"/>早秋氣臨時樹葉黃。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783b23"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783b2301" rend="margin-left:1em">僧問百丈惟政禪師云牛頭未見四祖時為甚麼
<lb ed="J" n="0783b24"/>百鳥啣花獻師云有錢千里通云見後為甚麼不
<lb ed="J" n="0783b25"/>啣花師云無錢隔壁聾。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783b26"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783b2601">一段春光炤眼鮮攀花弄柳任溪邊時人須識東君
<lb ed="J" n="0783b27"/>意莫向枝頭覓翠妍。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783b28"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783b2801" rend="margin-left:2em">百丈普請鉏地次僧聞鼓鳴歸院因緣。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783b29"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783b2901">鼓聲纔動競頭奔卉木俱霑雨露恩重勘過眼中釘
<lb ed="J" n="0783b30"/>百花叢裏覓鮮新。</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0783c" n="0783c"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0783c01"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783c0101" rend="margin-left:2em">百丈因一僧哭入法堂因緣。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783c02"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783c0201">哭上法堂草深一丈一時埋卻野狐伎倆匝匝清風
<lb ed="J" n="0783c03"/>撲面來舒襟樂意頻收放。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783c04"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783c0401" rend="margin-left:2em">百丈惟政禪師問南泉諸方善知識還有不說
<lb ed="J" n="0783c05"/>似人底法也無泉曰有政曰作麼生泉曰不是
<lb ed="J" n="0783c06"/>心不是佛不是物<note place="inline">云云</note>。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783c07"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783c0701">一問一荅真機漏洩更欲重徵喬木生節寒凝遍佈
<lb ed="J" n="0783c08"/>兮霜花朵朵黃葉飄零兮朔風凜冽。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783c09"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783c0901" rend="margin-left:1em">僧問百丈智映寶月禪師云師唱誰家曲宗風嗣
<lb ed="J" n="0783c10"/>阿誰月云窣堵那吒掌上擎<note place="inline">云云</note>。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783c11"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783c1101">窣堵掌上擎覿面<anchor xml:id="beg_7e" type="cb-app"/>已<anchor xml:id="end_7e"/>分付更欲問如何特地成露布
<lb ed="J" n="0783c12"/>不露布初生孩子元無褲。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783c13"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783c1301" rend="margin-left:2em">百丈道恒禪師三訣因緣。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783c14"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783c1401">喫茶珍重歇時人眼中屑若喚作三訣重添第二月
<lb ed="J" n="0783c15"/>穿衣褁腳下禪床運水搬柴知時節。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783c16"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783c1601" rend="margin-left:2em">百丈惟古禪師上堂多虛不如少實。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783c17"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783c1701">一卓一語機用雙舉更問如何大虫捉鼠。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783c18"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783c1801" rend="margin-left:2em">百丈中靖元肅禪師塔。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783c19"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783c1901">尖尖聳青虛巍巍磨太古欲識渠儂言但看清風舞。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783c20"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783c2001" rend="margin-left:2em">漁家傲題船子夾山因緣。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783c21"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783c2101">一語合頭猶未徹禪師笑倒纔方革劈面三橈君<anchor xml:id="beg_7f" type="cb-app"/>已<anchor xml:id="end_7f"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0783c22"/>瞥眼中屑回顧頻頻繫木橛。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0783c23"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0783c2301">覆卻舟兒真剿絕夾山從此偷心歇兩岸蘆花飛白
<lb ed="J" n="0783c24"/>雪向誰說幾度秋光與明月。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0783c25"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0783c2501" rend="margin-left:2em">又頌。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0783c26"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0783c2601">金鱗<anchor xml:id="beg_80" type="cb-app"/>已<anchor xml:id="end_80"/>遇意偏攸誠老何曾覆卻舟萬古清風波浪
<lb ed="J" n="0783c27"/>吼依然蘭棹在中流。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783c28"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783c2801" rend="margin-left:1em">僧問夢筆禪師如何是佛師云不誑汝僧云莫便
<lb ed="J" n="0783c29"/>是麼師云汝誑他。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0783c30"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0783c3001">寂寂沉沉無所倚全提覿面莫能擬春風散盡桃花
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0784a" n="0784a"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0784a01"/>飛秋月影臨江水止。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784a02"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784a0201" rend="margin-left:1em">閩王延夢筆禪師齋王問曰好將得筆來也無師
<lb ed="J" n="0784a03"/>云不是稽山繡管慚非月裏兔毫大王既垂顧問
<lb ed="J" n="0784a04"/>山僧敢不通呈。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784a05"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784a0501">覿面通呈非兔毫輕分閩主不辭勞梅花吐處春香
<lb ed="J" n="0784a06"/>露煦日纔臨冰質消。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784a07"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784a0701" rend="margin-left:1em">王又曰如何是法王師曰不是夢筆家風。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784a08"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784a0801">不是家風一句機偷香暗裏有誰知千峰布列須彌
<lb ed="J" n="0784a09"/>勢萬派宗分大海歸。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784a10"/><p cb:type="head2" xml:id="pJ26p0784a1001">雲門三種獅子<note place="inline">師居雲門室中作</note></p>
<lb ed="J" n="0784a11"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784a1101" rend="margin-left:1em">入窟獅子。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784a12"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784a1201"><anchor xml:id="beg_81" type="cb-app"/>斂<anchor xml:id="end_81"/>跡藏形古壑中豈尋聲色受華榮聖凡掃卻無依
<lb ed="J" n="0784a13"/>倚斗柄星河霽碧空。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784a14"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784a1401" rend="margin-left:2em">出窟獅子。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784a15"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784a1501">爪牙抖擻望天關哮吼一聲碧嶂寒魔外不知何處
<lb ed="J" n="0784a16"/>去威靈耿耿落人間。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784a17"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784a1701" rend="margin-left:2em">不出不入獅子。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784a18"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784a1801">窟內未曾留形跡人間那得有聲名石筍抽條千丈
<lb ed="J" n="0784a19"/>碧泥花發豔四時春。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784a20"/><p cb:type="head2" xml:id="pJ26p0784a2001">圓覺經頌</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0784a21"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784a2101" rend="margin-left:2em">文殊章。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784a22"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784a2201">本起如來清淨因桃紅柳綠一般春凡夫不了元無
<lb ed="J" n="0784a23"/>我病眼空花認作真圓炤婆伽親指示依然幻翳眼
<lb ed="J" n="0784a24"/>中生文殊當下知消息石女峰頭喚故人。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784a25"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784a2501" rend="margin-left:2em">普賢章。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784a26"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784a2601">幻化元來生覺心春風微動水生鱗時人但見波濤
<lb ed="J" n="0784a27"/>滾豈識波濤全體真有覺還同如幻立若緣無覺鏡
<lb ed="J" n="0784a28"/>中痕兩重公案都除卻天柱峰頭蓮萼新。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784a29"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784a2901" rend="margin-left:2em">普眼章。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784a30"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784a3001">漸次修行滅幻門火風地水究元辰忽然突出孃生
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0784b" n="0784b"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0784b01"/>面剎剎塵塵總是春擲柳黃鶯歌上苑穿花杜宇遶
<lb ed="J" n="0784b02"/>南林泥人翫月思情美石女簪花巧樣新。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784b03"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784b0301" rend="margin-left:2em">金剛藏章。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784b04"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784b0401">金剛抉破三疑網幻戲場中脫卻衣若說本來成佛
<lb ed="J" n="0784b05"/>道挖瘡好肉事非宜只因蒙昧難開曉金喻重重說
<lb ed="J" n="0784b06"/>是非識得上林花滿地風翻蝶舞過東籬。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784b07"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784b0701" rend="margin-left:2em">彌勒章。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784b08"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784b0801">起心若欲斷輪迴荊棘叢生覺地迷夢去雖然諸種
<lb ed="J" n="0784b09"/>事醒來何有半毫微若能寤寐都拈<anchor xml:id="beg_82" type="cb-app"/>卻<anchor xml:id="end_82"/>撒手懸崖好
<lb ed="J" n="0784b10"/>作為銕犬山中呼萬歲泥猿樹上唱囉哩。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784b11"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784b1101" rend="margin-left:2em">清淨慧章。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784b12"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784b1201">聲聞魔佛及菩薩正眼觀來總是邪朕兆未分難話
<lb ed="J" n="0784b13"/>會鴻濛<anchor xml:id="beg_83" type="cb-app"/>已<anchor xml:id="end_83"/>判念心差千紅萬紫筵青嶂總是陽春一
<lb ed="J" n="0784b14"/>氣嘉踢破乾坤收腳轉回頭別有好生涯。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784b15"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784b1501" rend="margin-left:2em">威德自在章。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784b16"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784b1601">突出乾城三觀門止啼黃葉卻非真新人乍出梳粧
<lb ed="J" n="0784b17"/>巧莫認衣裳要認人戲水遊魚知水意穿花蝴蝶味
<lb ed="J" n="0784b18"/>花深長安一曲有餘樂野老君王共太平。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784b19"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784b1901" rend="margin-left:2em">辨音章。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784b20"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784b2001">二十五輪遍互修一輪於內作根繇列開寶網光相
<lb ed="J" n="0784b21"/>映影現重重無盡頭四塞八蠻朝帝主兩京七地總
<lb ed="J" n="0784b22"/>皇猷鄉村野老茶鹽足一曲昇平樂事稠。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784b23"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784b2301" rend="margin-left:2em">淨諸業障章。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784b24"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784b2401">萬象收歸古鑑中我人生命盡消融空中飛鳥無形
<lb ed="J" n="0784b25"/>跡水底遊魚有甚蹤出岫浮雲何處往乘風花瓣任
<lb ed="J" n="0784b26"/>西東回頭忽聽木人鼓魄散魂飛沒影蹤。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784b27"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784b2701" rend="margin-left:2em">普覺章。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784b28"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784b2801">作止任滅聽從為休將四法取圓基平懷一種隨高
<lb ed="J" n="0784b29"/>下大道從來沒是非碧嶂野花開似錦石人觀去絕
<lb ed="J" n="0784b30"/>惺迷妙開寶印空中起印印何曾半點非。</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0784c" n="0784c"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0784c01"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784c0101" rend="margin-left:2em">圓覺章。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784c02"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784c0201">上下中期結制修鈍根須假煆塵浮大鵬翼展沖霄
<lb ed="J" n="0784c03"/>漢豈類鴳鶉落草坵十世古今頃一念誰能百日定
<lb ed="J" n="0784c04"/>程途狸奴白牯咸知有飢則餐兮渴飲流。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784c05"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784c0501" rend="margin-left:2em">賢善首章。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784c06"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784c0601">三世如來一口宣流傳須要善賢兼能聞一句勝多
<lb ed="J" n="0784c07"/>寶羅漢難同半偈肩不是天然生就覺又非觀行始
<lb ed="J" n="0784c08"/>成圓鷺鷥昨夜沙汀宿分付漁翁仔細看。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784c09"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784c0901" rend="margin-left:2em">總。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784c10"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784c1001">一道靈光貫古今剎塵俱是一毛吞獨超物表離名
<lb ed="J" n="0784c11"/>相阿個能言圓覺心一自伽婆分旨後千燈千炤續
<lb ed="J" n="0784c12"/>燈新孑蘆隨海飄波去熊耳峰頭花滿岑。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784c13"/><p cb:type="head2" xml:id="pJ26p0784c1301">首楞嚴經要頌</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0784c14"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784c1401" rend="margin-left:2em">大佛頂。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784c15"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784c1501">三德圓明非形相直教佛祖也難觀一聲胡笛邊營
<lb ed="J" n="0784c16"/>外幾處凄涼幾處歡。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784c17"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784c1701" rend="margin-left:2em">首楞嚴王。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784c18"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784c1801">一相該通空劫前河沙功德孰能宣超然不屬青黃
<lb ed="J" n="0784c19"/>色了了無依當處玄。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784c20"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784c2001" rend="margin-left:2em">七處徵心。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784c21"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784c2101">七處徵來七處真鷓鴣啼在百花林遊人沉醉桃園
<lb ed="J" n="0784c22"/>裡昧卻枝頭好鳥音。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784c23"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784c2301" rend="margin-left:2em">五陰。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784c24"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784c2401">真如迷卻翻成妄相妄空時當處真收拾伽缶歸去
<lb ed="J" n="0784c25"/>後白牛耕破劫前春。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784c26"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784c2601" rend="margin-left:2em">六入。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784c27"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784c2701">一團空聚無彼此痴兒妄自別疏親堂堂天子登朝
<lb ed="J" n="0784c28"/>日六國文明賀太平。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784c29"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784c2901" rend="margin-left:2em">十二處。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0784c30"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0784c3001">塵塵三昧首楞嚴擬心取著早乖遷月穿潭底非形
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0785a" n="0785a"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0785a01"/>相痴子徒勞摸碧川。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785a02"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785a0201" rend="margin-left:2em">十八界。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785a03"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785a0301">本來一相無疆界那許其間物我分十八疑關齊擊
<lb ed="J" n="0785a04"/>碎滔滔流水下滄溟。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785a05"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785a0501" rend="margin-left:2em">七大。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785a06"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785a0601">事理交參周法界將心擬處涉流沙情塵識破元無
<lb ed="J" n="0785a07"/>事木馬遊春意自賒。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785a08"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785a0801" rend="margin-left:2em">聲塵圓通。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785a09"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785a0901">妙音本自無來去聞聲悟入<anchor xml:id="beg_84" type="cb-app"/>已<anchor xml:id="end_84"/>成虛直須透徹聲前
<lb ed="J" n="0785a10"/>韻浩浩紅塵任卷舒。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785a11"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785a1101" rend="margin-left:2em">色塵圓通。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785a12"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785a1201">色色塵塵淨法身秪因憎愛昧天真苟能觸處通消
<lb ed="J" n="0785a13"/>息堪笑沙陀入聖倫。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785a14"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785a1401" rend="margin-left:2em">香塵圓通。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785a15"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785a1501">妙香元不從天降爇向爐中塞碧虛觸著些兒頭腦
<lb ed="J" n="0785a16"/>裂衲僧巴鼻盡蠲除。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785a17"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785a1701" rend="margin-left:2em">味塵圓通。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785a18"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785a1801">古今一味平胃散點著通身冷汗流慶快怡然拋藥
<lb ed="J" n="0785a19"/>病那容更犯死貓頭。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785a20"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785a2001" rend="margin-left:2em">觸塵圓通。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785a21"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785a2101">能洗所洗性本然驀頭一潑觸光圓器界根身渾一
<lb ed="J" n="0785a22"/>色輝輝秋月炤中天。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785a23"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785a2301" rend="margin-left:2em">法塵圓通。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785a24"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785a2401">心緣既寂法塵空事事全彰振古風東嶺桃花紅爍
<lb ed="J" n="0785a25"/>爍西溪流水響鼕鼕。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785a26"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785a2601" rend="margin-left:2em">眼根圓通。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785a27"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785a2701">見色非關眼上能時人休向眼中親應知那律非循
<lb ed="J" n="0785a28"/>目智鑑圓明耀古今。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785a29"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785a2901" rend="margin-left:2em">耳根圓通。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785a30"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785a3001">反觀聞性性俱空頓入圓明顯妙功歷歷松聲連夜
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0785b" n="0785b"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0785b01"/>吼呱呱鳥語亂山中。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785b02"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785b0201" rend="margin-left:2em">鼻根圓通。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785b03"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785b0301">循空返息本非真翻身踏倒涅槃城紅日舒光來嶺
<lb ed="J" n="0785b04"/>畔清風明月過溪濱。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785b05"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785b0501" rend="margin-left:2em">舌根圓通。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785b06"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785b0601">身心世界兩相遺覿體全超知不知處處總成真法
<lb ed="J" n="0785b07"/>界禪兒何事苦尋追。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785b08"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785b0801" rend="margin-left:2em">身根圓通。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785b09"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785b0901">無痛痛覺覺亦空根身從此影無蹤出門不踏來時
<lb ed="J" n="0785b10"/>路方顯男兒志氣沖。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785b11"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785b1101" rend="margin-left:2em">意根圓通。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785b12"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785b1201">物物頭頭本自真何須旋法美空生寶明空海人元
<lb ed="J" n="0785b13"/>具桃李爭妍處處春。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785b14"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785b1401" rend="margin-left:2em">眼識圓通。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785b15"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785b1501">心見圓明處處彰白雲閒矣水偏忙為憐頞下生盲
<lb ed="J" n="0785b16"/>者權示漚和演妙常。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785b17"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785b1701" rend="margin-left:2em">耳識圓通。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785b18"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785b1801">無心聞處是心聞塵剎全彰這個人百億分身無去
<lb ed="J" n="0785b19"/>相六牙常在寶王城。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785b20"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785b2001" rend="margin-left:2em">鼻識圓通。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785b21"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785b2101">鼻端白相示修行暫爾權為縳犢繩忽然摸著娘生
<lb ed="J" n="0785b22"/>鼻林泉巖谷悉光明。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785b23"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785b2301" rend="margin-left:2em">舌識圓通。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785b24"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785b2401">奇哉妙舌自天然不假喉唇齒吻宣無孔笛吹清韻
<lb ed="J" n="0785b25"/>徹滿慈謾謂得親傳。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785b26"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785b2601" rend="margin-left:2em">身識圓通。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785b27"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785b2701">身本無根何用執心本無生何用息身心寂滅兩俱
<lb ed="J" n="0785b28"/>空透此方名真法質。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785b29"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785b2901" rend="margin-left:2em">意識圓通。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785b30"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785b3001">一段情城當下除神通遊戲總無拘塢中昨日濛濛
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0785c" n="0785c"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0785c01"/>雨嶺上今朝日色舒。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785c02"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785c0201" rend="margin-left:2em">地大圓通。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785c03"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785c0301">根身器界若微塵微塵空處即天真堪<anchor xml:id="beg_85" type="cb-app"/>羨<anchor xml:id="end_85"/>頂門開正
<lb ed="J" n="0785c04"/>眼大千沙界一齊平。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785c05"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785c0501" rend="margin-left:2em">水大圓通。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785c06"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785c0601">滔滔流水性真常若個於斯返故鄉直於山海忘能
<lb ed="J" n="0785c07"/>所蝴蝶穿花過粉墻。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785c08"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785c0801" rend="margin-left:2em">火大圓通。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785c09"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785c0901">凡火慾火智慧火清淨寶焰光裸裸大千閃爍熾穹
<lb ed="J" n="0785c10"/>窿燃卻佛魔與物我。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785c11"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785c1101" rend="margin-left:2em">風大圓通。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785c12"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785c1201">群動悉憑風力持反觀風力亦無依忽然踏著風中
<lb ed="J" n="0785c13"/>主飄飄一葉過南池。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785c14"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785c1401" rend="margin-left:2em">空大圓通。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785c15"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785c1501">色空本自一真空逐境迷心有異同異同炤破真空
<lb ed="J" n="0785c16"/>現翻轉真空跨鐵龍。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785c17"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785c1701" rend="margin-left:2em">見大圓通。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785c18"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785c1801">六根清淨生元佛六根妄染佛為生見覺圓明生佛
<lb ed="J" n="0785c19"/>淨個中那有樂邦名。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785c20"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785c2001" rend="margin-left:2em">識大圓通。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785c21"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785c2101">十方唯識鏡中痕但離取捨妙圓成頭頭盡是天真
<lb ed="J" n="0785c22"/>佛念念全彰阿逸身。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785c23"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785c2301" rend="margin-left:2em">圓滿菩提歸無所得。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785c24"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785c2401">元宵通夜家家火水月交光處處圓五十七番虛涉
<lb ed="J" n="0785c25"/>後始知空費草鞋錢。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785c26"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785c2601" rend="margin-left:2em">總。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785c27"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785c2701">二十五個鐵蒺藜頭阤拶作雪花飛綠水溶溶歸巨
<lb ed="J" n="0785c28"/>壑白雲片片遶須彌。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0785c29"/><p cb:type="head2" xml:id="pJ26p0785c2901">金剛經要頌</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0785c30"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0785c3001" rend="margin-left:2em">世尊著衣持缽。</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0786a" n="0786a"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0786a01"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786a0101">一段風光秪在斯著他依舊不為奇清風陣陣飄香
<lb ed="J" n="0786a02"/>至碧水滔滔畫翠眉。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0786a03"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786a0301" rend="margin-left:2em">應如是住。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0786a04"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786a0401">搬柴運水尋常事覿面無非是道場觸處盡成安樂
<lb ed="J" n="0786a05"/>地何須此外更啇量。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0786a06"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786a0601" rend="margin-left:2em">如是降伏其心。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0786a07"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786a0701">著衣喫飯任從為映色摩尼眾像隨但得有無諸念
<lb ed="J" n="0786a08"/>淨金烏依舊落城西。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0786a09"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786a0901" rend="margin-left:2em">實無眾生得滅度者。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0786a10"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786a1001">空花鏡像了無關擬欲援生墮鐵山踏破瞿曇關捩
<lb ed="J" n="0786a11"/>子風自清兮雲自閒。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0786a12"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786a1201" rend="margin-left:2em">不住於相。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0786a13"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786a1301">祖印高提不住中巍然大用有無空騰騰任運靡存
<lb ed="J" n="0786a14"/>跡霧鎖秦宮絕雁鴻。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0786a15"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786a1501" rend="margin-left:2em">應無所住而生其心。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0786a16"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786a1601">坐斷兩頭中莫立逢緣擊節任縱橫摩尼現色原非
<lb ed="J" n="0786a17"/>有石筍開花映水紅。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0786a18"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786a1801" rend="margin-left:2em">無我人眾生壽者。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0786a19"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786a1901">木子山中敲鼓鑼泥人拍手助高歌忽逢瞽叟來瞧
<lb ed="J" n="0786a20"/>見滿面慚惶沒柰何。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0786a21"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786a2101" rend="margin-left:2em">四果不作是念。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0786a22"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786a2201">設分位次隔參商息卻名心絕短長若是威音親嫡
<lb ed="J" n="0786a23"/>子不從這裡費啇量。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0786a24"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786a2401" rend="margin-left:2em">燃燈佛所於法實無所得。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0786a25"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786a2501">倚門傍戶走他鄉雲水將來作道場倏爾踏翻潭底
<lb ed="J" n="0786a26"/>月了無一法贈劉郎。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0786a27"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786a2701" rend="margin-left:2em">持四句偈得福甚多。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0786a28"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786a2801">家藏白澤勝神符百怪安能敢穢污若得空王真號
<lb ed="J" n="0786a29"/>令三千諸佛作驅奴。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0786a30"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786a3001" rend="margin-left:2em">歌利王割截身體。</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J26.B188.0786b" n="0786b"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0786b01"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786b0101">忍辱功能作聖人幻成四大卻非真任他節節支離
<lb ed="J" n="0786b02"/>去一段風流獨露身。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0786b03"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786b0301" rend="margin-left:2em">一念信心即得菩提。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0786b04"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786b0401">棄家浪走不如屠自昧千金七寶軀偶爾忽逢長者
<lb ed="J" n="0786b05"/>示凡心即與聖心符。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0786b06"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786b0601" rend="margin-left:2em">受持讀誦此經若為人輕賤一節。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0786b07"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786b0701">念念輸忠不敢違色聲叢裡了無羈苔封古殿忘臣
<lb ed="J" n="0786b08"/>主阿個能言佛祖機。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0786b09"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786b0901" rend="margin-left:2em">三心不可得。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0786b10"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786b1001">兔角為刀出遠征烏龜跨下羽毛生木童拔去搓繩
<lb ed="J" n="0786b11"/>索縛住虛空架火烹。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0786b12"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786b1201" rend="margin-left:2em">無法可得。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0786b13"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786b1301">三藏靈文不較多權將音語示娑婆忽地雙林開正
<lb ed="J" n="0786b14"/>眼試問還曾有也麼。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0786b15"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786b1501" rend="margin-left:2em">如來說非眾生是名眾生。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0786b16"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786b1601">生佛從來共一程凡民何必<anchor xml:id="beg_86" type="cb-app"/>羨<anchor xml:id="end_86"/>公卿如能當下歸家
<lb ed="J" n="0786b17"/>也凡聖原來是假名。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0786b18"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786b1801" rend="margin-left:2em">如來者無所從來亦無所去。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0786b19"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786b1901">一念緣生即是遊靡分紅紫有何愁威音那畔元無
<lb ed="J" n="0786b20"/>動今世門頭示兩眸。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0786b21"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786b2101" rend="margin-left:2em">總。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0786b22"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786b2201">忉忉怛怛老婆禪失卻瞿曇臉半邊四相掃除無一
<lb ed="J" n="0786b23"/>物呼名般若亦縺涎。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0786b24"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786b2401" rend="margin-left:2em">法華經頌<note place="inline">二</note>。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0786b25"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ26p0786b2501">三乘不立一也無三一元來醒夢夫若是空王殿上
<lb ed="J" n="0786b26"/>客撒手歸來月滿湖。</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0786b27"/><p xml:id="pJ26p0786b2701">妙法不在聲名上尊者徒勞授記功欲識個中端的
<lb ed="J" n="0786b28"/>意桃花卻白李花紅。</p></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0786b29"/>
